  Source:
    Title: Yoga-Vasishtha
Tags:
  - 941
---
Flying is no business of the spiritual yogi, who is concerned only with a
knowledge of the Spirit; he is content with his spiritual knowledge and union
with the Supreme, and does not meddle with the practices of the ignorant
and false Hatha-Yogis.
